name: One-Bedroom-Suite-Queen---600sqf---56sqm-
alt: This photo showcases out 600 square foot suite bedroom with a Queen size bed against the wall and a seating bench at the foot of the bed. Across from the bed there is a six drawer dresser and a wall mounted 42 inch flat screen TV. Adjacent to the dresser is the full size Italian marble bathroom. The bedroom also features a full size closet with mirrored sliding doors. French doors will lead to the living room which features a full size bar, three bar stools and a wall mounted flat screen 42 inch TV.
